Hi liencf,

We=E2=80=99ll be performing scheduled maintenance this Sunday, November 2, =
2025, as part of a major platform upgrade.

During this time, the entire Topcoder platform will be unavailable for appr=
oximately 6 hours, starting at 1:30 AM EST.

This maintenance marks a huge milestone - we=E2=80=99re officially saying g=
oodbye to Informix after 24 years and moving to a simpler, faster, and more=
 reliable platform built on modern technology.

